                     <interp inst="t18181028-112-off647" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18181028-112-cd648" type="crimeDate">16th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18181028-112-off647 t18181028-112-cd648"></join>, eight books, value 29s.; one pair of scales and weights, value 7s. 6d.; fifteen copper tokens, value 6d.; fifteen medals, value 1s., and one bag, value 1s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18181028-112-victim825" type="victimName">
                  Thomas 
                  Schofield
               <interp inst="t18181028-112-victim825" type="surname" value="Schofield"></interp>
